cs.NI, cs.DB, cs.CR, cs.DS, cs.AI 

The paper discusses big data analytics for large-scale wireless networks, which involves the acquisition, preprocessing, storage, and analysis of large volumes of data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses data storage and analysis, which are related to database systems (cs.DB) and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses security challenges in wireless networks (cs.CR) and machine learning techniques for data analysis (cs.AI).
